channel.title: So, what exactly did Casey do?
channel.description:
In his nomination topic in the Veteran Polls section, everyone is talking about some bad shit he did in the past. Despite me being in MoparScape for quite a long time now, I wasn't among the "elite" (you guys) until semi-recently.
So, what did Casey actually do that people can't get over?
